comments: Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Jokic (DEN) jumps alongside Strus' (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of an offensive basket interference on Butler (MIA) stands.  Butler makes contact with the ball while it is still in the imaginary cylinder above the basket ring.
Adebayo (MIA) moves into Cancar (DEN) during the screen and dislodges him from his position.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Strus's (MIA) path and does not deliver contact.
Butler (MIA) exits the paint within three seconds.
Vincent (MIA) legally contests Brown's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) briefly grasps Jokic's (DEN) arm underneath the rim and slides his hand off as they both pursue the loose ball.
Martin (MIA) turns to roll and marginal contact occurs with Brown (DEN) as Brown goes over the pick.
Adebayo (MIA) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) places his hand to Adebayo's (MIA) side and marginal body contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Vincent's (MIA) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Adebayo (MIA) jumps alongside Brown (DEN) and cleanly blocks his driving shot attempt.
Cancar (DEN) brushes Adebayo's (MIA) arm at the end of his drive and he is able to move through the marginal contact to complete his pass.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs to Jokic's side as he defends over the pick.
Cancar (DEN) jumps vertically and absorbs the incidental contact initiated by Strus (MIA).
Vincent (MIA) is moving alongside Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Caldwell-Pope's drive to the basket.
Butler (MIA) moves laterally into Caldwell-Pope's (MIA) path and makes incidental leg to leg contact after the release of his pass.
Cancar (DEN) and Vincent (MIA) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Brown (DEN) and Strus (MIA) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as they move through the screen.
Jokic (DEN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Brown (DEN) briefly places a hand on Strus (MIA) and immediately slide his hand off without applying force while defending his jump shot attempt.
Cancar (DEN) and Vincent (MIA) engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Vincent (MIA) commits a take foul on Braun (DEN).
Brown (DEN) immediately slides his hand off of Strus' (MIA) side and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Braun's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.

Brown (DEN) makes contact to Strus's (MIA) shoulder in an attempt to get to the ball and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.  The illegal contact occurs before Brown makes contact with the ball.
Bryant (DEN) places his arm to Butler's (MIA) side underneath the basket and marginal body contact occurs as they pursue the long rebound.
Vincent (MIA) commits a take foul on Brown (DEN).
